1.4
log
@Remove port of 13 year old fxtv release.

suggested by landry, ok dcoppa and benoit
@
text
@FXTV provides TV-in-a-window and image/audio/video capture capabilities
for Brooktree-based tuner/capture cards through the Brooktree video
capture driver, bktr(4). It can take advantage of direct video and DGA.
FXTV can perform video and audio capture, and run a script to assemble
captured data into an audio/video MPEG stream.
@


