1.1
log
@fxtv 0.48: TV viewer for the bktr driver.
@
text
@d1 5
a5 3
   Fxtv is an X11-based OpenBSD app that provides TV-in-a-window and
   image/audio/video capture capabilities for Bt848/878-based tuner/capture
   cards.
d7 1
a7 8
   To use this app, you need OpenBSD 2.4 or above as well as a capture card
   based on the Brooktree 848/878 chip.
   Examples include the Hauppauge Wincast/TV, the STB TV PCI,
   and the Intel Smart Video Recorder III.

   The Fxtv home page is http://www.freebsd.org/~rhh/fxtv

   Refer to the README for details on usage
@

